  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis</h2>In this Point & Click game you'll play as a father in search of his beloved son. You will have to face little challenges and big choices to find him and bring him back to the safety of home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477900/extras/f94722d5e1744f8c94966a5b72f4ab49.avif?t=1607081777\" width=411 height=415 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2>In this Point & Click graphic adventure, you'll need to solve puzzles and decide the actions that Ricky must follow.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477900/extras/c3581f6a7b46d28def142e0cc161c56c.avif?t=1607081777\" width=192 height=238 /></span>",
